=head2 B<REQUIRED> NotificationType => Str

The Type of the event causing this notification.

=over

=item *

Values:

=over

=item *

C<ALERT>

=over

=item *

A notification about an event where something was triggered, initiated,
reopened, deployed, or a threshold was breached.

=back

=item *

C<WARNING>

=over

